criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Women aged 20 to 45;

          2. BMI > 19 & < 35;

          3. Women who is planning to perform invitro fertilization (IVF) together with
             intracytoplasmic sperm injection (ICSI) for their fertility problems

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Positive pregnancy test before taking study medications;

          2. Women with BMI>35 kg/m2;

          3. Women with known chromosomal translocation, recurrent abortions or those carrying
             Fragile X;

          4. Women with endometriosis
